<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>AWS na Nuvem - Deploy na EC2</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    header {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      padding: 1.5rem 5%;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ff9900;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 4rem auto;
      padding: 0 5%;
      text-align: center;
      flex: 1;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #ff9900;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #ff9900;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .card-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    .card h3 {
      color: #ff9900;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    footer {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: auto;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
      h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="logo">AWS na Nuvem</div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Deploy na AWS EC2</h1>
    <p>Bem-vindo ao meu servidor rodando na <span class="highlight">Amazon Web Services</span>!</p>
    <p>Esta página está hospedada em uma instância <span class="highlight">EC2</span> com Node.js, PM2 e deploy via Git.</p>

    <div class="card-container">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Por que EC2?</h3>
        <p>Escalabilidade, controle total, custo baixo e alta disponibilidade.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
        <p>Node.js • Express • PM2 • Git • Nginx (opcional)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Status</h3>
        <p>Online 24/7 • IP Público: <strong>Seu IP aqui</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Próximos passos</h2>
    <p>Adicionar HTTPS (Let's Encrypt), CI/CD com GitHub Actions, monitoramento com CloudWatch e auto-scaling!</p>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>Feito com ☁️ e muito café | Deploy na AWS EC2 | 2025</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>